; ------------------------------------------------------------
; Finish-order resolver (executor 24, after the race)
; ------------------------------------------------------------
; Spawned once all 6 horses have crossed the line. For each of
; the 6 positions, checks whether any horse has a placement code
; already assigned there; otherwise it increments horseNProgress
; and sorts horses by their progress counters to pick the winner
; at each position. The big block of permutation branches below
; handles every horse-vs-horse comparison. Writes final placements
; to gRaceFinishOrder[2..5].

